    - The battle was initiated by  [
Muzaffar Jung](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Muzaffar_Jung) + [Joseph François Dupleix](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Joseph_Fran%C3%A7ois_Dupleix) + led by [Chanda Sahib](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Chanda_Sahib), who sought to overthrow -[Anwaruddin Muhammed Khan](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Anwaruddin_Muhammed_Khan),  ([Nawab of the Carnatic)](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Nawab_of_the_Carnatic) for supporting [Nasir Jung](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Nasir_Jung)'s claim to be [Nizam of Hyderabad. = ](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Nizam_of_Hyderabad)French forces were decisive in giving the allies victory; Anwaruddin Muhammed Khan was killed in the battle and Chanda Sahib seized control of the Carnatic.
